title: Quality Convo with Neil DeGraide of Dirt Poor Robins -  Processes & Music, Pirsig & Orthodoxy
description:
The fascinating Visionary, Neil DeGraide of the singular band Dirt Poor Robins,  shares the story of his unique life and artistic trajectory! We discuss Neil's upbringing, his early musical giftedness, meeting his artistic soul mate, and the propensity he has for uniting spirit & symbolism with all his artistic projects: music, film, literature and visual...plus we sprinkle in Pirsig here and there.

Website: https://www.dirtpoorrobins.com/
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuQZw5EE__gCljrkm0sBCOw
